reviews.review_text: crispy! this is the version you want - very crispy!
4-15-78 Wonderful sound and musiciianship. C Miller does it again.

Searching for the Sound... Fantastic performance, jaw-dropping audio quality.  (Mr. Miller, you are a God....)

For those of you in the right "frame of mind" searching for THE show to listen to, this one will not disappoint.

Good luck in treetops.   :-)

William&Mary 78' This is a killer show with high energy and exceptional playing.very nice half-step opener starts a gr8 first set.set 2 is just awesome with a gr8 playin'.the nfa>morning dew is off the charts.a must listen despite sunrise..lol.
Brown Eyed Women ? I like the show and the sound is good but the B.E. Women has such a strange beat.    I can't even tap my foot along with the drums, not sure why they were playing it this way.
